data.description: Welcome to your exquisite haven of modern luxury and rustic charm! This fully renovated 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom bungalow epitomizes the perfect blend of sophistication and comfort. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the allure of the luxury vinyl flooring, offering both durability and style, complemented by the sleek granite countertops in the kitchen. The elegant pine wood accents throughout the home add a touch of warmth and character, creating a cozy ambiance that invites you to unwind and enjoy the comforts of home. Venture further into the living space, and you'll discover a built-in entertainment center where the 65-inch flatscreen Samsung TV awaits. This thoughtful addition enhances the living area, providing a seamless focal point for entertainment while maximizing space efficiency. In addition to the interior upgrades, this bungalow boasts a new metal roof and siding, ensuring both durability and curb appeal for years to come. Inside and out, no detail has been overlooked, with updated plumbing and electrical systems offering peace of mind and modern convenience. Outside, your fully fenced backyard provides a private retreat, perfect for hosting gatherings with loved ones or simply soaking up the serene surroundings. Step out onto your expansive 15x11 back deck, a delightful space for outdoor entertaining or simply enjoying a morning coffee while overlooking your lush surroundings. Whether you're seeking a tranquil escape or a space to entertain, this meticulously renovated bungalow offers the perfect combination of luxury, comfort, and convenience. Every detail has been carefully curated to enhance your lifestyle, making this home a true sanctuary where you can create cherished memories and indulge in the finer things in life. Welcome home to a world of refined living!
